'''Wedderveer''' ({{IPA-nl|ˌʋɛdərˈveːr}}) is a [[hamlet (place)|hamlet]] near [[Wedde]] in the municipality of [[Westerwolde (municipality)|Westerwolde]] in the [[Netherlands]]. It has a population of around 135 and a total area of {{convert|47|ha|acres|abbr=on}}.<ref name="cbs"/>

The [[sawmill]] [[Spinnenkop Wedderveer|Spinnenkop]] has been listed as a [[Rijksmonument|national heritage site]] since 1990.<ref>{{nl icon}} [http://monumentenregister.cultureelerfgoed.nl/php/main.php?cAction=show&cOBJnr=388083 Monumentnummer: 388083 - Spinnekop], [[Rijksdienst voor het Cultureel Erfgoed]]. Retrieved on 27 April 2014.</ref>

